>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <iframe \n    width=\"560\" \n    height=\"315\" \n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dvTgIbiwHqc?autoplay=1&mute=1\" \n    title=\"YouTube video player\" \n    frameborder=\"0\" \n    allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture\" \n    allowfullscreen>\n  </iframe>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin:6px 0;\">\n    <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\" alt=\"features\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin:2px 0 4px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/punchy\">\n    <img \n      width=\"750\"\n      src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d205b6380c63f1e8d075fbcd727d40dcdee15c0b.webp\" \n      alt=\"Punchy x Bisect Hosting Banner\"\n    />\n  </a>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Divider BELOW banner -->\n<div style=\"margin:4px 0 6px 0;\">\n  <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\" alt=\"features\"/>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<img width=\"30%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/47e0f59a12115269646e828a6f7c65f7139efce1.webp\" alt=\"Better Combat\">\n<br>\n<br>\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/8aoMKplv/images/3a29acf139bff97b6abe147602ee3b7aea626620.gif\" alt=\"Better Combat\">\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;\">\n  <p>\n    For the <b>best compatibility</b> with Better Combat addons, use this resource pack:\n  </p>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/punchy!-compatibility\">\n    <img width=\"80px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b5b655780b2e2a45f484af6e93f268e0c677357c.png\" alt=\"features\" />\n  </a>\n  <br>\n  <i>Click to view</i>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin:6px 0;\">\n    <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\" alt=\"features\"/>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div>\n    <img width=\"300px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9c571a5ef1176c92ce66a7157c33dd1779420632.png\" alt=\"features\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;\">\n  <p>\n    Instead of individual resource packs,<br> all <b>explicit Punchy! compatibility features</b>\n    are maintained in a single Modrinth collection.\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    This collection is kept up to date and includes officially recommended compatibility packs.\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin:16px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/collection/GypBAs4y\">\n    <img width=\"320\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1295a4a95570fdd19437f2af3d6edb9ef0cf9cd1_0.webp\" alt=\"Punchy! Compatibility Collection\" />\n  </a>\n  <p style=\"margin-top:6px;\"><i>Click to view the full Modrinth collection</i></p>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"margin:6px 0;\">\n    <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\" alt=\"features\"/>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img width=\"400px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2bb0d76282288d92aa6d210cac2db4384ac8f439.png\" alt=\"features\" />\n\n<section>\n  <h3>Credits</h3>\n  Godku for all the help.<br>\n  Jaredlll08 for the multiloader template:\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/jaredlll08\">Jaredlll08 Github Page</a><br>\n  Lunggolfs for the Social Connect Icons Pack:\n  <a href=\"https://lunggolfs.itch.io/social-connect-icons-pack\">Lunggolfs Site</a><br>\n  CRV6 for the trailer and the amazing music:\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@CRV6-Music/featured\">CRV6 Youtube Channel</a><br>\n  Craftandoof for the awesome wake up animation:\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/craftandoof\">Craftandoof Modrinth Profile</a><br>\n  themodderg for the clean, iconic mod icon:\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/themodderg\">themodderg Modrinth Profile</a><br>\n  c